### Change product name and price
PATCH http://localhost:5000/product/fbbf6840-5ba4-11ea-a188-0242c0a83003
Content-type: application/json; charset=UTF-8

{
    "name": "New product name",
    "price": 1.99
}

### Return products list, page = 1, per_page = 10
GET http://localhost:5000/products

### Return products list, page = 2, per_page = 5
GET http://localhost:5000/products?per_page=5&page=2

### Return product info by id
GET http://localhost:5000/product/fbbf6840-5ba4-11ea-a188-0242c0a83003

